      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pahr to Gada Behrnu\nZilts Spehku bija Eelisaws/De-\nguêta Dehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad zehlahs tee Kaâtiteri/\nnesdami tahs fwehtas Leetas/ un\n(tee zitti) uszehle to Dsihwokli/\nkamehr schee nahze.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pehz to zehlahsEewrâi-\nma Behrnu Lehgera Karrohgs/\npehz faweem Pulkeem/ un pahr\nwinna Spehku bija Eelisamus/\nAmjuda Dehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pahr to Manaffus\nBehrnu Zilts Spehku bija Gam-\nliêts/ Pedazura Dehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pahr to Benjamina\nBehrnu Zilts Spehku bija Abi-\ndans/ Gideonza Dehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad zehlahs tas Danna\nBehrnu Lehgera Karrohgs/fatur-\nredams winus Lehgerus / pehz\nwinzu Pulkeem/ un pahr winna\nSpehku bija Akiësers / Ammi-\nSadaja Dehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pahr to Ahsera Behr-\nnu Zilts Spehku bija Pagîêls /\nOkrana Dehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pahr to Nawtaka\nBehrnu Zilts Spehku bija Aki-\nrus/ Eenana Dehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schee bija to Israëta\nBehrnu Zelta -Gahjumi / pehz\nwinzu Pulkeem / kad tee zehlahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Mohsus fazzija us O-\nbabu / Reguêta ta Midjaniters\nDehtu/ Mohsus Snohtu: Mehs\neetam us to Weetu / no ka tas\nKUNGS fazzijster: To es jums\ndobfchu / eij lihds ar mums / jo\nmehs griƀbam tew labdarriht/ jo\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "tas KUNGS irr Israëtam Lab-\nbunu apfohlijis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija : Es ne\neeschn / bet us fawu Semmi/ un\npee manneem Raddeim gribbu es\neet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tas fazzija us winnu:\nNe atstahji no mums/ jo tapehz\ntâ tu muhsus Zelta-Gahjumus\nTuksneti finni / tad tew buhs\nmums par Azzi buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas notiks / ja tu ar\nmums ceţi / un tas Labbums\nmums nahks/ar ko tas KUNGS\nmums labbi darrihs / griƀbam\nmehs tew arridsan labbu darriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad zehlahs tee no ta\nKUNGA Kalna / treijo Deenu\nZelta-Gahjumu/ un ta KUNGA\nDerribas Schkirsts gahje win-\nneem preefschâ treijo Deenu Zet-\nta-Gahjumu / weenu duffamu\nWeetu winneem rahdiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta KUNGA Padeb-\nbes bija Deenâ pahr winneem /\nkad tee no ta Lehgera zehlahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas notike / kad tas\nSchkirsts zehlahs / tad fazzija\nMohsus: Zellees KUNGS / un\nlaid tawee Eenaidneeki iskaifiti\ntohp / un tawee Eenihdetaji lai\nbehg preefsch tawu Waign.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad wiꞥſch duffeja/ tad\nfazzija wiꞥſch:AtgreefeesKUNgs/\nvee teem tuhkfoscheem Israëta\nPulkeem.\n"
    }
  ],
